%; }\n            .d-flex {\n                display: flex;\n            }\n            .d-flex-col {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .left{\n                float : left;\n            }\n            .right{\n                float : right;\n            }\n            .center {\n                margin-left: auto;\n                margin-right: auto;\n            }\n            .all-caps {\n                text-transform : uppercase;\n            }\n            .bg-grey {\n                background-color: #f1f1f1;\n            }\n            .text-center {\n                text-align: center;\n            }\n            .mx-1rem {\n                margin-right: 1rem;\n                margin-left: 1rem;\n            }\n            .my-1rem {\n                margin-top: 1rem;\n                margin-bottom: 1rem;\n            }\n            .m-all-1rem {\n                margin: 1rem;\n            }\n            .newsletter-header {\n                font-size: 1.5rem;\n                font-weight: bold;\n            }\n            .newsletter-link {\n                margin: 1rem;\n                text-decoration: none;\n                color: white;\n            }\n            .newsletter-btn {\n                border : 2px solid #FFFFFD;\n                padding: 0.5em 0.5em;\n                background-color: #add8e6;\n            }\n            .newsletter-btn:hover {\n                /*background-color: #68828a;*/\n                background-color: #8aadb8;\n            }\n        </style>\n    \n    \n        <!-- Static navbar -->\n        <div class=\"navbar navbar-default\" role=\"navigation\">\n            <div class=\"container\">\n                <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n                    <!-- ADD YOUR SELLER NAME OR LOGO HERE -->\n                    <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Deals Only</a>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"navbar-collapse collapse\">\n                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav navbar-right\">\n                        <!-- ADD MENU LINKS HERE. THESE ARE NON-FUNCTIONAL EXAMPLES. -->\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\">Our Store</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/usr/dealsonlywebstore\">About Us</a></li>\n                        <li><a href=\"https://contact.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?ContactUserNextGen&amp;recipient=dealsonlywebstore\">Contact Us</a></li>\n                    </ul>\n                </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <div>\n                    <div class=\"main-image\">\n                        <img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/usurper-products/48685/6pc_gold_testing_kit.jpg\" class=\"img-responsive\" alt=\"Responsive image\">\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <h3>Product Details</h3>\n                <!-- ADD A NEW ROW FOR EACH PRODUCT ATTRIBUTE YOU WANT TO SHOW IN THE TABLE OR YOU CAN REMOVE THE TABLE COMPLETELY-->\n                <div class=\"product-specs\">\n                    <table>\n                        <tbody>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">MPN:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right\">TTDLXATGKS8</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">UPC:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right\">810131708412</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPLETE GOLD TESTING KIT: Easily test the karat content of gold with ToolTreaux’s Complete Gold Testing Kit! The kit includes four, 0.5oz shatterproof plastic squeeze bottles, a neutralizing solution and one gold testing stone; the testing solutions are potent, effective and will see you through hundreds of tests</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">GOLD TESTING KIT METHOD: This gold testing method is best used on gold that is yet to be smelted, due to the harsh nature of the solution that could potentially damage an already finished item; if testing fine jewelry or other finished gold items, be sure to choose an inconspicuous spot so as not to compromise the finished piece</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">HOW THE GOLD TESTING KIT WORKS: To test gold karat content and purity, scratch the item onto the test stone leaving a visible deposit, then place a small drop of the solution over top of deposit; if the gold is the same karat or higher the solution will not affect the deposit; if the deposit is of a lower karat, the deposit will dissolve and eventually disappear</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS: Testing Stone Dimensions: 2 x 1.5 x 0.25 inches; Stone Weight: 0.01lbs; Bottle Dimensions: 3 x 1 x 1 inches; Bottle Weight: 0.04lbs; Bottle Material: Plastic; Solution Capacity: 0.5 ounces; Solution made in USA</td>\n                            </tr>\n                            <tr>\n                                <td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n                                <td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">NOTE: Keep out of reach of children; Use caution when opening and using; Proper protective gloves and eyewear are highly recommended; Instruction pamphlet included</td>\n                            </tr>\n                        </tbody>\n                    </table>\n                </div><!-- /product-specs -->\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-md-6\">\n                <h1>ToolTreaux 6pc 10k 14k 18k 22k Complete Gold Testing Kit with Testing Stone</h1>\n                <h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">34.99</span></h2>\n                <p>Easily test the karat content of gold with ToolTreaux’s Complete Gold Testing Kit! The kit includes four, 0.5 ounce (oz) bottles with 10k, 14k, 18k and 22k solutions, a neutralizing solution and one gold testing stone. The testing solutions are potent, effective and will see you through hundreds of tests! A must-have tool for gold panning, jewelry appraisal or other professions that work with gold and precious metals. And, housed in small, sturdy, shatterproof plastic squeeze bottles, the gold testing solution bottles are comfortable to maneuver, while also easily maintaining control over the amount of solution escaping the bottle.\n\nGOLD TESTING KIT METHOD: This gold testing method is best used on gold that is yet to be smelted, due to the harsh nature of the solution, that could potentially damage an already finished item; if testing fine jewelry or other finished gold items, be sure to choose an inconspicuous spot so as not to compromise the finished piece \n\nHOW THE GOLD TESTING KIT WORKS: To test gold karat content and purity, scratch the item onto the test stone leaving a visible deposit, then place a small drop of the solution over top of deposit; if the gold is the same karat or higher the solution will not affect the deposit; if the deposit is of a lower karat, the deposit will dissolve and eventually disappear; ensure gold testing stone has been thoroughly washed before completing any testing.\n\nPLEASE NOTE: Exercise the utmost caution when opening and using this product and method of testing! Proper protective eye wear and gloves are highly recommended, as the solution can burn unprotected skin. Read the label on the bottle and follow the included operational instructions. Keep out of Reach from Children.</p>\n                <div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n                    <div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-100\">\n                        <p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n                        <p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n                        <a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><!-- /col-md-6 -->\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 footer\">\n                <p>© 2025</p>\n            </div> <!-- /footer -->\n    \n        </div> <!-- /container -->\n        <div style=\"clear:both\">\n            &nbsp;<table></table>\n        </div>\n",
